    "Organizational artificial intelligence (AI)-based approaches to develop and engage can customize and effectively connect with users during periods of high demand.",
    "Targeting Gen Y and Gen Z The primary demographic groupings that makeup TikTok's user base in Thailand are Generation Y (individuals aged 22-38 years) and Generation Z (individuals aged 17-22 years) (Marketing Guru, 2022).",
    "The aforementioned demographic characteristics are a strategic approach to appealing to diverse age cohorts by offering a wide range of content options.",
    "Business enterprises can customize their endeavors and engage with these two demographic cohorts, acknowledging their status as the TikTok platform's most engaged and participatory user segments.",
    "The comprehension of the demographic characteristics of TikTok users in Thailand facilitates the development of material that possesses qualities of sophistication, contemporaneity, and attractiveness, thereby catering to the preferences of individuals belonging to both Generation Y and Generation Z."
